description: All our dishes are prepared from beginningto end in-house. We cook with the finestingredients from small Artisan producers inSpain, following traditional recipes that I havebeen using all my life - this is very important tous and we think it makes the difference!﻿We bring you Tapas from the richly varied regional cuisines of Spain from Galicia to Andalucía, the Basque Country to Cataluña.Enjoy!
name: Simply Spanish  Tapas and Paella
